{"tid":1373561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚴正呼籲】冷氣軍師請盡量唔好向前線下達指令","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T02:14:54.000Z","uid":184643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"198e78b70c32e85be1f8514392b8f54d47a22d43","tid":1373561,"uid":184643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"首先好多謝你哋嘅關注同建議<br />\n<br />\n但係前線撤唔撤謂俾番前線決定<br />\n冷氣軍師係重要，不過體現喺資訊<br />\n係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">資訊</span></strong>呀!<br />\n邊度有大量狗集結<br />\n警方戰術佈防<br />\n邊度交通癱瘓<br />\n有旗無旗<br />\n邊度有退路，甚至安全撤離路線<br />\nfact check 等等<br />\n哩啲都係其他人所做唔到嘅事<br />\n請冷氣軍師多做哩啲<br />\n<br />\n對前線下達指令，只會造成<span style=\"color: red;\">混亂</span>，久而久之會<span style=\"color: red;\">造成不信任</span>㗎!<br />\n<br />\n除非啲狗迅速集結形成包圍，否則請盡量減少指令，唔該哂!<br />\n<br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e64a8c90fbd715b89faf779554d9181bcc5b8ba","tid":1373561,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:52:59.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家入去填低感受</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經收左集超過二百人嘅感受，幫我地推到上一千、二千 OK ？</span></span><br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3669c6139b393debc68a89d0e6766eae1097df9","tid":1373561,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:14:54.000Z","msg":"其實我諗緊分析埋個結果有冇必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我覺得唔分析結果係好啲嘅<br />\n<br />\n利申有去元朗冇叫人走"}]}